* Turner, Henry Ashby ''German Big Business and the Rise of Hitler'', New York: Oxford University Press, 1985 ISBN 0-19-503492-9.
* Wheeler-Bennett, Sir John ''The Nemesis of Power: German Army in Politics, 1918-1945'', New York: Palgrave Macmillan Publishing Company, 2005 ISBN 1-4039-1812-0.
* Edgar Ansel Mowrer ''Germany Puts The Clock Back'', John Lane The Bodley Head, London ,1933 and ''Triumph and Turmoil'', George Allen & Unwin,1968
* Arthur Rosenberg ''A History of The German Republic'', Methuen, London, 1936.
{{refend}}

